---
// Componente Hero
---

<section class="relative bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 pt-24 pb-16 lg:pt-28 lg:pb-24">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 place-items-center">
            <!-- Left: copy -->
            <div class="text-left">
                <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight text-gray-900 mb-6 max-w-2xl">
                   La invitación de matrimonio
                    <br />
                    <span class="text-lovio-500">digital más hermosa</span>
                    <br />
                    que hayas visto
                </h1>

                <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg lg:text-xl mb-8 max-w-xl">
                    Diseños únicos e interactivos, comparte al instante. 
                    <span class="font-semibold text-lovio-600">Tu día perfecto merece una invitación increíble.</span>
                </p>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
                    <button class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-base font-semibold shadow-lg hover:bg-lovio-600 transition-colors">
                        Crear invitación
                    </button>
                    <a href="#como-funciona" class="text-lovio-500 font-semibold underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-lovio-600">
                        ¿Cómo funciona?
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: phone mockup -->
            <div class="relative flex justify-center">
                <div class="relative w-[220px] sm:w-[240px] md:w-[260px] aspect-[9/19] rounded-[2.5rem] bg-black/90 shadow-2xl ring-8 ring-black/5 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mt-3 w-28 h-6 bg-black/60 rounded-full"></div>
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741497674-611481863552?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Vista previa de invitación" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
                        <a href="#ejemplo" class="bg-white/90 text-gray-900 backdrop-blur px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold shadow hover:bg-white transition">
                            Ver ejemplo
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-40 bg-gradient-to-b from-pink-100/60 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
</section>
